snippet.title: Prodeus : Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Prodeus is the first person shooter of old, re-imagined using modern rendering techniques. It reaches the quality you expect from a AAA experience while adhering to some of the aesthetic technical limits of older hardware.

Join our community and add us to your Steam Wishlist!

Website: http://www.prodeusgame.com
Twitter: https://twitter.com/ProdeusGame
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/964800/Prodeus/
Discord: https://discord.gg/GY3gCQU

Being developed by :
Mike Voeller - @RealtimeVFXMike
Jason Mojica - @Generalvivi

Music by: Andrew Hulshult
